---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Affiliate Disclosure";
const description = "How Gear Versus Tech earns commission through Amazon Associates, eBay Partner Network, and Awin affiliate programmes.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
<div class="container">
  <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span class="current">Affiliate Disclosure</span></nav>
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p class="article-meta-line">Last updated: July 2026</p>

  <h2>How We Earn Money</h2>
  <p>Gear Versus Tech participates in affiliate marketing programmes. When you click a link to a retailer and make a purchase, we may receive a commission. This comes at no additional cost to you.</p>

  <h2>Programmes We Participate In</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. Amazon and the Amazon logo are trademarks of Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates.</li>
    <li><strong>eBay Partner Network</strong> — We are a member of the eBay Partner Network. eBay links on this site direct you to eBay.co.uk.</li>
    <li><strong>Awin</strong> — We participate in the Awin affiliate network, linking to direct-to-consumer brands.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Does This Affect Our Recommendations?</h2>
  <p>No. Our comparisons and reviews are based on product specifications, testing, and real-world performance data. We do not accept payment for rankings, and commission rates do not influence our verdicts. A product that earns us a higher commission will never be recommended over a better product that earns less.</p>

  <h2>How to Identify Affiliate Links</h2>
  <p>All outbound product links on Gear Versus Tech are affiliate links unless otherwise stated. You can identify them by:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>URLs containing <code>tag=gearversustech-21</code> (Amazon)</li>
    <li>URLs containing <code>campid=5339164583</code> (eBay)</li>
    <li>The <code>rel="nofollow sponsored"</code> attribute on all affiliate link elements</li>
    <li>Buttons labelled "Check Price on Amazon" or "Find on eBay"</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Price Information</h2>
  <p>Prices displayed on Gear Versus Tech are checked regularly but may change at any time. Always confirm the current price on the retailer's website before making a purchase. We do not guarantee the accuracy of pricing information displayed on this site.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For questions about our affiliate relationships: <a href="mailto:hello@gearversustech.com">hello@gearversustech.com</a></p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
